Package: ddsdashboard
Title: Explore and Process RNA-seq DESeqDataSet Objects
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Siwat Chad", "Ruangroengkulrith", email = "chorchatty@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny dashboard for exploring, manipulating, and visualizing
    bulk RNA-seq results stored in DESeqDataSet (and convertible
    SingleCellExperiment) objects. Aimed at users with little to no
    bioinformatics background: quality control, metadata editing,
    filtering, normalization, dimensionality reduction, DESeq2
    differential expression, heatmaps, and export. Also exposes reusable
    helper functions (normalization, feature lookup) for other projects.
